0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97e1c4aad767e1093fbf835c44b2d694adcea99","tid":1538922,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"呢樣我OK"},{"pid":"0515b93ff87b6c20a9b3d6e61cd9200059c300ba","tid":1538922,"uid":57776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"9973eac03323cfa0954d304f9ff5426c180b9fe3","tid":1538922,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"咪開埋晒d垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6c2c17f1b71d75e41d791bd495a776b27c7f62","tid":1538922,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br 